Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就那樣進入了彎道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...地出了彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一瞬間 我就是風的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.76,0:01:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山道果然很爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.53,0:01:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們買車之後也去試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是車手們嚮往的85啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過外行是不懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.78,0:02:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(158,261)\fs20\fad(650,900)}來自超級巨星的挑戰書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.17,0:02:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年夏天太有衝擊力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.93,0:02:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼什麼意思 意思是我買了車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而拓海有如彗星般的首次亮相賽車界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一 二 三 四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在數什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這個夏天獲勝的比賽數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先是REDSUNS高橋啟介的FD吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著是Night Kids中裏的32
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.31,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有和莊司慎吾EG6的膠帶死亡賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.52,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後就是上次在碓冰真子和沙雪的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四戰全勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是藤原拓海不敗神話的開始之夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.43,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從普通的呆瓜漸漸轉變過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼大驚小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別害羞嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要繼續贏下去 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到本大爺打敗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並被稱為群馬...不...關東最快的那天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為秋名的流星 樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.96,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海 今天只有開學典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.27,0:04:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下午去玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.92,0:04:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可下午要去打工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打工啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想再乘一次拓海的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你說可愛...那也只是老爸的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 你說過想買車吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢存得怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打工的錢幾乎都存起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可離目標還差得遠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要存多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多一百萬左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一百萬啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那現在有多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿一百萬圓給你的話會怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超感謝我 把我的事看得無比重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.86,0:05:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後滿腦子都是我 不去打工 每天陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變得超級恩愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 討厭 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.27,0:05:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這種小鬼哪裏搞得到一百萬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呀...只是打個比方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想像一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太異想天開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之一點很明顯拓海的技術在哪兒都適用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是技術的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第一次跑的道路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能馬上跑得飛快 還是要靠天生的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直是天才啊 面對新型高性能機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用十年前的86也能全勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.69,0:06:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得好聽 不久前你明明說拓海只跑過秋名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到別的地方會很慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是...別提這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都會這麼想的 是拓海太特別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說他去碓冰比賽時我也認為絕對不可能贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對真子的Sil-80...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事 請別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.62,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是孤獨車手池谷嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是樹的台詞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞錯了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是加油站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 是給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰送的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高橋涼介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高橋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涼介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.63,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,群馬NO.1的超級巨星...送給拓海?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫什麼? 我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.96,0:07:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九月十五日 晚上十點 秋名山頂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就寫了這些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...那就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來自高橋涼介的下山賽挑戰書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼怎麼樣 事到如今只能接受了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,REDSUNS的弟弟高橋啟介輸給了拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 如果逃避雪恥賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.24,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比輸掉還可恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我在一起不高興嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就心不在焉嘛 在那兒發著呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然平時也這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過感覺你心思不在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然那麼無聊 我就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不無聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.45,0:08:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那告訴我你在想什麼 不說的話就不原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算說了 我想你也很難明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.37,0:08:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 知道了 我說就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼? 要打架?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.28,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦 用車子來競賽就是我說的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用車子來競賽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不知道你還有這種愛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不算是愛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不覺就變成這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.80,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這次的對手非常厲害 是個名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從早上起就一直在考慮 心裏放不下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是所謂的壓力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你駕駛得很好 沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那麼簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不願意的話 不去不就行了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不知道能不能贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我確實沒想過逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有這樣的一面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實心裏躍躍欲試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.12,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表很老實 骨子裏卻是絕不認輸的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不討厭這種性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.02,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.81,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再等會兒 再說會兒話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...我其實知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在足球部的活動室...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和前輩打架的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.25,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你退部後 當時在場的一個同學悄悄告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.17,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海你是為了我生氣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 一直誤會你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在已經無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是拓海的86嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然厲害 土屋圭市的漂移
